# ============================================================================
# El Sanatorio POS chain proxies — 2026-06-20
# ============================================================================
# The POS chain (PWAs + Netlify Functions) lives in the maia-management repo
# at /vert/restaurant/sanatorio/{pos,pay,kitchen,floor,dice}/ and
# /.netlify/functions/sanatorio-*. We proxy from el-sanatorio.com (this
# site) to maia-management.com so staff QR codes + customer URLs can use
# the el-sanatorio.com domain (e.g. https://el-sanatorio.com/pay/<order_id>).
#
# Proxy status 200 means the URL stays on el-sanatorio.com in the address
# bar; behind the scenes Netlify fetches from maia-management.com.
#
# CRITICAL: when adding new POS routes, add them BEFORE the marketing-site
# redirects below — Netlify processes the first match.
# ============================================================================
/pos                            https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/pos/  200
/pos/                           https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/pos/  200
/pos/*                          https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/pos/:splat  200
/pay/:order_id                  https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/pay/?order_id=:order_id  200
/pay/:order_id/wompi            https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-wompi-checkout?order_id=:order_id  200
/dice                           https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/dice/  200
/dice/                          https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/dice/  200
/dice/:order_id                 https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/dice/?order_id=:order_id  200
/kitchen                        https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/kitchen/  200
/kitchen/                       https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/kitchen/  200
/floor                          https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/floor/  200
/floor/                         https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/floor/  200
/wompi-webhook                  https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-wompi-webhook  200

# Sanatorio POS API endpoints (used by the PWAs above)
/api/sanatorio-create-order            https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-create-order  200
/api/sanatorio-create-order-v2         https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-create-order-v2  200
/api/sanatorio-print-ticket            https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-print-ticket  200
/api/sanatorio-order-status            https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-order-status  200
/api/sanatorio-update-order-status     https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-update-order-status  200
/api/sanatorio-mark-paid-cash          https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-mark-paid-cash  200
/api/sanatorio-fake-pay                https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-fake-pay  200
/api/sanatorio-dice-roll               https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-dice-roll  200
/api/sanatorio-dice-claim              https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-dice-claim  200
/api/sanatorio-dashboard-feed          https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-dashboard-feed  200
/api/sanatorio-wompi-checkout          https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-wompi-checkout  200
/api/sanatorio-wompi-webhook           https://maia-management.com/.netlify/functions/sanatorio-wompi-webhook  200

# Shared PWA assets (CSS, JS, fonts, images used by pos/pay/kitchen/floor/dice)
# REQUIRED — without this rule /pay and /dice render blank because brand.css +
# menu.js are referenced as absolute /vert/restaurant/sanatorio/shared/* paths.
# Fix landed 2026-06-24 PM.
/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/shared/*  https://maia-management.com/vert/restaurant/sanatorio/shared/:splat  200

